 "contentEncoded": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3487/3192038647_b36071c996.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>It&#x2019;s so cold outside, we&#x2019;re doing everything we can to stay warm. We&#x2019;ve asked you about your <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/28/you-tell-us-whats-your-favorite-warm-winter-drink-in-town/\" target=\"_blank\">favorite belly-warming wintery drinks</a> before, but now we&#x2019;re on a quest to hunt down the best cup of hot chocolate in town (thanks to a query by our friend <a href=\"http://twitter.com/justwinston/status/7453865278\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Winston</a>). Responses have been pouring in on Twitter, with <a href=\"http://www.thecocoatree.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.thecocoatree.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Cocoa Tree</a> emerging as a clear leader &#x2013; But don&#x2019;t let that sway your vote!</p>\n<p><strong>So tell us, what&#x2019;s the best cup o&#x2019;cocoa in town?</strong> (If we left your favorite off the list, a thousand apologies, but that&#x2019;s why the &#x201C;Other&#x201D; option is there.)</p>\n<div id=\"polls-12\" class=\"wp-polls\">\n\t<form id=\"polls_form_12\" class=\"wp-polls-form\" action=\"/2010/01/06/you-tell-us-home-of-the-best-hot-chocolate-nashvillest-polls/\" method=\"post\">\n\t\t<p style=\"display: none;\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"poll_id\" value=\"12\"></p>\n\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What&apos;s the best cup o&apos;cocoa in Nashville?</strong></p><div id=\"polls-12-ans\" class=\"wp-polls-ans\"><ul class=\"wp-polls-ul\">\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-77\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"77\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-77\">The Cocoa Tree</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-78\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"78\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-78\">Portland Brew</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-79\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"79\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-79\">Frothy Monkey</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-80\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"80\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-80\">Bongo Java</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-81\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"81\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-81\">Mike&apos;s Ice Cream Fountain</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-82\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"82\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-82\">Ugly Mugs</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-83\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"83\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-83\">Crema</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-84\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"84\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-84\">Fido</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-85\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"85\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-85\">Cafe Coco</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-86\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"86\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-86\">ChaChah (seriously!)</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-87\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"87\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-87\">Dunn Bros</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-88\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"88\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-88\">Maxximo Jo&apos;s (in Franklin)</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-89\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"89\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-89\">The Perch (in Brentwood)</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-90\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"90\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-90\">Starbucks</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-91\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"91\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-91\">I make the best hot chocolate ever, suckers</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-92\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"92\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-92\">Other</label></li>\n\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-93\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"93\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-93\">Dose</label></li>\n\t\t</ul><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><input type=\"button\" name=\"vote\" value=\"   Vote   \" class=\"Buttons\" onclick=\"poll_vote(12);\" onkeypress=\"poll_result(12);\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/01/06/you-tell-us-home-of-the-best-hot-chocolate-nashvillest-polls/#ViewPollResults\" onclick=\"poll_result(12); return false;\" onkeypress=\"poll_result(12); return false;\" title=\"View Results Of This Poll\">View Results</a></p></div>\n\t</form>\n</div>\n<div id=\"polls-12-loading\" class=\"wp-polls-loading\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-polls/images/loading.gif\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Loading ...\" title=\"Loading ...\" class=\"wp-polls-image\">&#xA0;Loading ...</div>\n\n<p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/barl0w/3192038647/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Scott Barlow</em></a><em>. </em></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/06/29/you-tell-us-whats-the-best-place-to-watch-fireworks-nashvillest-polls/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: You Tell Us: What&#x2019;s The Best Place To Watch Fireworks? [Nashvillest Polls]\">You Tell Us: What&#x2019;s The Best Place To Watch Fireworks? [Nashvillest Polls]</a></li>\n</ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"
